#. module: sign_itsme
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/sign_itsme/static/src/components/document_signable.js:0
msgid ""
"The itsme® identification data could not be forwarded to Odoo, the signature"
" could not be saved."
msgstr ""
"ຂໍ້ມູນການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນ itsme® ບໍ່ສາມາດສົ່ງຕໍ່ໄປຍັງ Odoo ໄດ້, ບໍ່ສາມາດບັນທຶກການລົງນາມໄດ້."

#. module: sign_itsme
#: model:ir.model.fields.selection,name:sign_itsme.selection__sign_item_role__auth_method__itsme
msgid "Via itsme®"
msgstr "ຜ່ານ itsme®"

#. module: sign_itsme
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/sign_itsme/static/src/components/document_signable.js:0
msgid ""
"You have rejected the identification request or took too long to process it."
" You can try again to finalize your signature."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານໄດ້ປະຕິເສດຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນ ຫຼື ໃຊ້ເວລາດົນເກີນໄປໃນການປະມວນຜົນ. ທ່ານສາມາດລອງໃໝ່ອີກຄັ້ງເພື່"
"ອເຮັດການລົງນາມໃຫ້ສຳເລັດ."

